nodes.text: Star Wars: Galaxy's Edge trading cards

Star Wars: Galaxy's Edge trading cards are a set of trading cards themed around Star Wars: Galaxy's Edge. They were given out at two "Star Wars Galactic Nights" events in December 2017 and May 2018. When combined as a full set, the backs of each card create a map of Black Spire Outpost.
Some of the cards also had alternate versions with the text in Aurebesh.
